n come from {\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname place}}{\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname City}}Swansea{\*\xmlclose}{\*\xmlclose}. But the world of Rotary, and also, did I miss Freemasonry?  I don\rquote t know.  I don\rquote 
