}}{\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname City}}Swansea{\*\xmlclose}{\*\xmlclose} people politically antipathetic in quite the same way, but the world of greengrocers and solicitors was quite hard for me to ge}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15552741 
