\ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15552741 n, it\rquote s an overdrawn contrast. }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244499 The great temptation in fieldwork, which is easy to criticise yourself for, is you do what\rquote s easy, and if it\rquote 
ll work. Although I did have the discipline of, you know, knowing all the addresses and trying to get data on everybody and all the rest of it, I didn\rquote t really reveal in either the book or the chapter \endash  that there\rquote 
