\rquote re aware, a piece of work at the same time as we were funded by the SSRC, on paternity leave, which is published by the Equal Opportunities Commission, called \'93Families, Childbirth and Work\'94, to see what happened \'85 and Lorna and I di
d do all the fieldwork for this.  We took every mother, serially, off the gynaecological conveyor belt at the Queen Elizabeth Hospital in Birmingham, and interviewed them and their partners about his leave-taking behaviour during her pregnancy, during the
