{\*\xmlclose}{\*\xmlclose}, well, I think it is. Bill just thought this was a charade, you know, and therefore didn\rquote t believe his fieldwork - you couldn\rquote t actually go and do that fieldwork in that sort of way.  And didn\rquote t Ronnie do }{
\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \i\insrsid14244499 Village on the Border}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244499  because he got chucked out of the copper belt?
