urveying the literature with any degree of efficiency, that there are loads of community studies being done out there.  I just suspect probably there are not, and I don\rquote 
t come across small town studies, or even studies of suburbs in quite the same way as there once were.  But it might be that the field\rquote 
s always been dying, that the Welsh socio-anthropologists thought there was never going to be any more, and I didn\rquote t think there was ever going to be any more, and that maybe th}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6696687 ere are. I don\rquote 
