\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \b\insrsid8917117\charrsid8917117 PAUL:\tab }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8917117 You made this interesting remark about how, you know, on the farms you saw lots of th
ings, you observed lots of things.  Can you give me the flavour?
