sed off that I was going to go.  They then rearranged, overtly, and we discussed it, and no one came to blows, the authorship reflects the labour, and }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \i\insrsid8917117 Property, Paternalism.}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
