, which is led by Rose.  There were some politics articles, which were Saunders.  I had two articles in the }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \i\insrsid8917117 Journal of Agricultural Economics}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8917117 
