\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \b\insrsid8917117\charrsid8917117 PAUL:\tab }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8917117 Would you say, by this point, he\rquote d changed a lot, then, or not?
