\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \b\insrsid8917117\charrsid8917117 PAUL:\tab }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8917117 But anyway, you remarried to Jan?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \b\insrsid8917117\charrsid8917117 COLIN:\tab }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8917117 
Yeah.  But leaving is quite interesting, because I took redundancy from Aston, did very little and worked in record shops and various things like that for a bit.  And Peter told me about this job at Leicester, called \'93Social Scientist\'94
 in the Leicester Medical School.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \b\insrsid8917117\charrsid8917117 PAUL:\tab }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8917117 Was there a gap, actually, between Aston and that?
