\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \b\insrsid8917117\charrsid8917117 COLIN:\tab }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8917117 Yeah, it\rquote s big, and the whole of the Sutherland\rquote 
s work on long-term care of the elderly and all that, it matters.  It matters.  And it even impressed Sutherland that I knew about some of this stuff.  So I did abandon it, and I felt guilty for a bit.  Mike Clarke and I have made it up.  Well, be
cause he says, \'93Not many of my research assistants become Vice-Chancellors!\'94  (LAUGHS)  So he dines out on it as well!
